    "title": "FabHotels is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "FabHotels invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of E-commerce Executive at our Visakhapatnam location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout FabHotels:\nFabHotels is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FabHotels!",
